                                            No matter if you are ordering a platter of comfort cuisine from a country of your choice or munching down on some good ole American junk food and a fusion Mixed Pot specialty; 
                                            it's going to be fresh and from a kitchen of love. That our promise here at The Mixed Pot LLC. 
